msgctxt "324"
msgid "Picking Up/Throwing Objects"
msgstr "Recogiendo / lanzando Objetos"

msgctxt "56_Picking Up/Throwing Objects"
msgid "Beer bottles and other debris from the road can be thrown at the enemy. Press <Action:Button_Circle@Chase> to throw the objects that you pick up."
msgstr "Las botellas de cerveza y otros escombros del camino se pueden lanzar al enemigo. Presiona <Action:Button_Circle@Chase> para lanzar los objetos que recojas."

